    ANKI

    Anki is a SRS tool that is based on flash cards. The main use of it is by medical students due to the sheer amount of facts they need to remember. 

    Zotero

    It is a Citation tool, that can also handle highlighting PDFs, creating scholarly citations, and integrating with several other services.

    My Study Life

    A tool to manage your hectic schedule for IB. You could try it or go on with the old fashion way of writing down dates and paper, and subsequently having them vanish in the ether.
